For Motor_blynk

Wiring Connections

Motor Driver â†’ Motors
IN1, IN2 â†’ Left Motor A
IN3, IN4 â†’ Right Motor B
Motor driver +12V â†’ Battery (+)
Motor driver GND â†’ Battery (â€“) + ESP32 GND

ESP32 â†’ Motor Driver
GPIO 26 â†’ IN1
GPIO 27 â†’ IN2
GPIO 14 â†’ IN3
GPIO 12 â†’ IN4
